# Claude Code — shared config is tracked (settings.json, agents/); local state is not.
# Verified 2026-07-16: settings.local.json (personal overrides) and
# scheduled_tasks.lock (runtime lock: sessionId/pid) are the only local artifacts
# Claude Code actually writes into a project's .claude/. Session todos live in
# ~/.claude/projects/<path>/<session-id>/, NOT here — a `.claude/todos/` rule was
# ignoring a path that has never existed in any of these repos.
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock

